profile:
We see our customers more than once a year because we provide all year long maintenance service starting from maintaining the windows and eavestroughs during the spring and fall. During the winter months we plow. We strive to establish and build long-term relationships with our customers that‘s why we take pride in ourselves on providing friendly, reliable service all year long.   
 
Here at Richview Windows & Eaves Cleaning Inc. we take pride on providing the best possible window and eavestrough clean. 
 
Our window clean includes washing frames, sills & scraping.
 
Our eavestrough clean includes the following: 
 
1. Clean all levels of eaves including the garage. 
 
2. Snake the downspouts, flush them with water and if the downspouts are really clogged we take the downspouts apart.
 
3. Includes removal of cages, full eavestrough and downspout inspection for any repairs .
 
4. Does not include removal of screens (leaf gourds) 
 
5. We also provide pictures and videos of our eavestrough clean upon customer request.
 
If we see any repairs that need to take place while we clean the eavestrough we notify our customer right away with pictures and videos and hereafter we leave a service recommendation inside the mailbox.
 
Richview alternative services available:
 - Exterior Painting 
 - Exterior Window Caulking
 - Power Washing
 - Eavestrough Installation/Repair
 - Exterior Eavestrough Cleaning  
 - Aluminum Soffit, Fascia & Flashing Installation/Repair    
 - Vinyl Siding Installation/Repair
 - Christmas Light Installation
 - Leaf Gourd Installation
 - Snow Removal

profile:
Bubbling With Pride In Our Work For You!

How does Suds outshine the competition? Well, for one thing, we don’t just wash and wipe!

Our people have an informed understanding of the complexities and challenges posed by the properties of different types of glass fibres. We’re also familiar with the mechanics and designs of windows, old and new - and how and why they are installed. 

Maybe you’ve never considered why those aspects of window cleaning are important. Why would you? Frankly, most other cleaners don’t, either. They just lather, rinse and repeat. 

The team at Suds understands how to go beyond those basics and you’ll see the difference shine through! 

We have amazing reviews because of our transparency - and that’s the crystal clear truth! 

As a matter of fact, our founder - who holds two university Engineering degrees - rolls his sleeves up right along with the team.

He visits clients’ homes and stays on top of new processes, learning up close and personal the different challenges that every type of home presents. That way, we always have the best solution for you. Because washing is about a lot more than just soap and water! 

Experience and talent can be found in every industry. But the Suds strategy for client satisfaction insists on those assets and puts an equal emphasis on high-level customer service skills demonstrated by every member of our team.

With so much to offer, Suds is constantly growing. But we make sure to provide our personal touch at every stop. Our clients recognize and respect that we wash with their pride and expectations in mind. 

And that never washes off!
